---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../../components/Navigation';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer';
import Chatbot from '../../components/Chatbot';

const lang = 'en';
const title = 'General Terms and Conditions of Use – Automatisons.fr';
const description = 'Terms of Service for the services offered by Automatisons Agence IA.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} lang={lang}>
  <Navigation lang={lang} isHomePage={false} client:load />

  <main class="pt-16">
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 text-gray-800">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-10">Terms of Service</h1>

      <p class="bg-yellow-100 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 text-yellow-900 px-4 py-3 mb-6">
        <strong>Important:</strong> These Terms of Service (ToS) govern the use of automation and artificial intelligence services provided by Automatisons Agence IA. They constitute a contract between you and our company.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">1. Purpose and Scope</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        These ToS define the conditions under which Automatisons Agence IA provides its automation, AI, and digital transformation consulting services. They apply to all orders placed via our website, by phone, email, or any other means.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">2. Definitions</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        <strong>"Automatisons Agence IA" or "Provider"</strong>: the company Automatisons Agence IA SAS<br />
        <strong>"Client"</strong>: any individual or legal entity ordering services<br />
        <strong>"Services"</strong>: automation, AI, consulting, and training services<br />
        <strong>"Project"</strong>: all Services defined in a quote or contract<br />
        <strong>"Deliverables"</strong>: the results of the Services provided to the Client
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">3. Order and Acceptance</h2>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-4">3.1 Order Process</h3>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Each order follows this process:
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
          <li>Free audit (48h)</li>
          <li>Customized quote (within 7 days)</li>
          <li>Client approval</li>
          <li>Contract signature</li>
          <li>Work begins</li>
        </ul>
      </p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-4">3.2 Acceptance</h3>
      <p class="mb-4">
        The order becomes final upon signature of the quote and receipt of the deposit. Automatisons Agence IA reserves the right to refuse any order that does not comply with these ToS.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">4. Pricing and Payment Terms</h2>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-4">4.1 Pricing</h3>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Prices are in euros excluding taxes. Any additional services will require a separate quote.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-4">4.2 Payment Terms</h3>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-4">
        <table class="min-w-full border border-gray-300 text-sm">
          <thead class="bg-gray-100">
            <tr>
              <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-left">Project Type</th>
              <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-left">Deposit</th>
              <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-left">Balance</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">&lt; €5,000</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">30% upon order</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">70% upon delivery</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50">
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">€5,000 – €20,000</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">40% upon order</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">60% upon delivery</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">&gt; €20,000</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">50% upon order</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">50% according to schedule</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-4">4.3 Late Payment</h3>
      <p class="mb-4">
        In case of late payment, penalties of 3% per month will apply. If payment is not received within 8 days, services may be suspended.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">5. Service Execution</h2>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-4">5.1 Deadlines</h3>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Deadlines are indicative and start upon receipt of the deposit and all required materials.
      </p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-4">5.2 Client Obligations</h3>
      <p class="mb-4">
        The Client agrees to provide necessary information and access, appoint a contact person, and validate deliverables on time.
      </p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-4">5.3 Provider Obligations</h3>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Automatisons Agence IA agrees to act professionally, maintain confidentiality, and provide support and training if agreed upon.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Custom developments become the Client's property after full payment. Generic tools remain the property of Automatisons Agence IA.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">7. Confidentiality</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Each party agrees to keep all exchanged information confidential for 5 years after the end of the contractual relationship.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">8. Warranties and Liability</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Automatisons Agence IA guarantees that Services will comply with defined specifications. It can only be held liable in case of proven fault.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">9. Applicable Law and Jurisdiction</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        These ToS are governed by French law. Any dispute will be subject to the competent courts of Paris.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">10. Contact</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        For any questions, you can contact us at:<br />
        Email: <a href="mailto:contact@automatisons.fr" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">contact@automatisons.fr</a><br />
        Address: 123 Avenue de l'Innovation, 75001 Paris, France<br />
        Phone: +33 6 48 09 15 11
      </p>

      <p class="mt-12 text-sm text-gray-500">Last updated: June 24, 2025</p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer lang={lang} client:load />
    {/*<Chatbot lang={lang} client:load />*/}
</Layout>
